<td sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Go to <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Fixed assets</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Depreciation profile</strong>. For a depreciation profile with <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Depreciation method</strong> = <code sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Straight line life remaining</code>, select the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Half year depreciation on additional acquisitions</strong> check box. If this option is switched on, depreciation convention <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="44">Half year (start year)</strong> is implemented for additional acquisitions.</td>
