<td sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Go to <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Fixed assets</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Fixed assets parameters.</strong> On the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">General</strong> tab, select <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Apply specific rules for half year depreciation</strong> and <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Automatically create depreciation adjustment amounts with disposal</strong>.</td>
