<h2 id="half-year-depreciation-on-additional-acquisitions-calculation" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Half year depreciation on additional acquisitions calculation</h2>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">When the <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Apply specific rules for half year depreciation</strong> and <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Automatically create depreciation adjustment amounts with disposal</strong> check boxes are marked, the depreciation adjustment amount for fixed assets with the <code sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Straight line life remaining</code> depreciation method and <strong sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Half year (start of year)</strong> convention, is posted automatically with the disposal that is calculated according to the half year convention rules.</p>
